topics.body:
So the vote on the Trans-Pacific Partnership is coming up; I hope it gets shot down again.

Short version of what the TPP is that it's a bill that's being marketed as "It's a progressive bill that would help out the USA; support it or else you're a dirty conservative who hates the poor". . . Yeah, no; the bill wouldn't do jack shit to help the working class, if anything it would fuck things up for the working class.

If someone here supports the TPP cause "It's a progressive bill" you're literally fucking retarded cause the bill would promote fracking and under it you wouldn't know what goes into your food, etc.

The TPP is SOPA 2.0 on crack.
